{
  "texts": [
    "Those results are consistent with the findings presented here.",
    "Our model correctly identified much of the internal content (Fig. 5a; r =.77, p < 0.001) and external content in autobiographical memories (Fig.",
    "5b, r =.80, p < 0.001).",
    "Internal content was not significantly misclassified as external content (Fig. 5c, r = -.08, p = 0.371), and external content was not often misclassified as internal content (Fig.",
    "5d, r =.21, p = 0.012)."
  ]
}